lead_paragraph: The Yankees appeared to be in sell-off mode at the non-waiver trading deadline, sending away starter Ivan Nova and top relievers Aroldis Chapman and Andrew Miller in what looked like a nod to the future.

headline.print_headline: Yankees Overcome 4-Run Deficit, Beat Royals 5-4 in 13
